milestones.description: Sompal Kami and Rohit Paudel's 52-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 38 between Vesawkar and Lamichhane
Sompal Kami has broken the record for most sixes (6) in ODIs for NEP, going past Kushal Malla's 5
Kiplin Doriga has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (4) in ODIs for PNG, going past Dogodo Bau's 3
Aarif Sheikh has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (11) for NEP, going past Airee
